        <briefdescription>
<para>Enables or disables toggle-by-click.   </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>When enabled, the <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1SelectableTrait" kindref="compound">SelectableTrait</ref> listens to the owner <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref>&apos;s ClickedSignal and toggles the selected state on each click. If the owner <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref> does not already have a <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1InteractiveTrait" kindref="compound">InteractiveTrait</ref>, one is automatically created and attached.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">enabled</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>True to enable toggle-by-click, false to disable   </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
